 New Translations Support

Ciao! We have now added Italian language support to some of our games!

Italian translations are available in:

-   Main Lobby
-   Murder Mystery
-   Skywars
-   Cops and Crims
-   Pixel Painters

We have also increased support for Brazilian Portuguese translations!

Brazilian Portuguese is now available in all of these modes:

-   Arcade
-   Bedwars
-   Main Lobby
-   Murder Mystery
-   Skywars
-   Housing
-   Parties
-   Pixel Painters
-   TNT Games

We plan on continuing to support more game modes for both languages, as well as Chinese Traditional, as they are done being translated.
